# Normalize all text files to LF in the repo. Working tree EOL is left to
# core.autocrlf, so Windows users still see CRLF locally if their git config
# says so. This avoids large CRLF/LF diffs between Linux CI and Windows devs.
* text=auto eol=lf

# Binary safeguards (none today, but ready when we add screenshots / pdfs).
*.png binary
*.jpg binary
*.jpeg binary
*.gif binary
*.pdf binary
*.zip binary
